        <section id="detailed_desc">
            <p>The callback for the second instance.</p>
            <dl outputclass="deprecated">
            <dlentry>
                <dt>Deprecated:</dt>
                <dd>Use <xref keyref="videoSourceConnectionStateChanged"/> instead.</dd>
            </dlentry>
            </dl>
            <p>The SDK triggers this callback when it loses connection with the server for more than four seconds after the connection is established. After triggering this callback, the SDK tries to reconnect to the server. You can use this callback to implement pop-up reminders. 该回调与 <xref keyref="videoSourceConnectionLost"/> 的区别是：



            <ul>
            <li><apiname keyref="videoSourceConnectionInterrupted"/>回调一定是发生在成功加入频道后，且 SDK 刚失去和服务器连接超过 4 秒时触发。</li>
            <li><apiname keyref="videoSourceConnectionLost"/>回调是无论是否成功加入频道，只要 10 秒内和服务器无法建立连接都会触发。</li>
            </ul>                如果 SDK 在断开连接后，20 分钟内还是没能重新加入频道，SDK 会停止尝试重连。</p>
        </section>
